title: Highway to Heaven - S01E15 - One Winged Angels
description:
15. One Winged Angels   
Community Score
8.1 Great
First aired: 1/16/1985

Jonathan has a tough time on this particular assignment. He is supposed to get Libby and earl to fall love with each 
other but Jonathan runs into one problem before he can accomplish the assignment he falls in love with Libby. Mark 
tells Jonathan that God may have wanted Jonathan to fall in love again so he wouldn&#039;t lose touch with what it&#039;s like to
 be a human being and feel how painful falling in love can be.

Writer: Jan Heininger, Hugh Corcoran
Director: Michael Landon
Guest star: Hugo Stanger (Mr, Gidden), Robin Dearden (Libby), John Lawlor (Earl), Peggy McCay (Louise), 
Wil Wheaton (Max)
